$PAR
Find the volume of the wedge-shaped region (Figure
1) contained in the cylinder \(x^2+y^2=\{$r**2\}\) and
bounded above by the plane \(z=x\) and below by the \(xy\)-plane.
$PAR
\{image("image_15_4_7_a.png", width=>263, height=>275)\} 
$PAR
